Seems to be related to my removal of HandyReturnValues. I will look into it!
Thanks for reporting! Did you found more Matcher that misbehave like that?

issue.title: Fixes #457 CompareTo compares now only agains instances of Comparable.

repository.name: mockito
repository.description: Most popular Mocking framework for unit tests written in Java

issue.body:
This PR...
- fixes the NPE described in #457 
- fixes cases were CCE were thrown if an `ArgumentMatcher`is not type-complatible with an argument to match.
- fixes parameter types in all constructors of `CompareTo`sub classes 
- added tests to `HashCodeAndEqualsSafeSetTest`in order to pass the codecov checks
